DiscountCodeDraft
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     DiscountCodeDraft discountCodeDraft = DiscountCodeDraft.builder()
             .code("{code}")
             .plusCartDiscounts(cartDiscountsBuilder -> cartDiscountsBuilder)
             .build()
